mapper.select: select from IOT_SEWAGECON_215 t,iot_deviceinfo u where u.di_serialnum=t.device_serialnum and (u.DI_DEACTIVE < 1 or u.DI_DEACTIVE is null) and u.di_nodeid = #{ORGId} order by u.di_serialnum asc
select from IOT_SEWAGECON_215 t,iot_deviceinfo u where u.di_serialnum=t.device_serialnum and u.di_serialnum = #{sDeviceId}

select
from IOT_DEVICEINFO a,IOT_HISSEWAGECON_215 b WHERE a.DI_SERIALNUM = b.DEVICE_SERIALNUM AND a.DI_SERIALNUM = #{deviceId,jdbcType=VARCHAR} AND b.SENDDATE >= to_date(#{startDate,jdbcType=VARCHAR},'yyyy-mm-dd hh24:mi:ss') AND b.SENDDATE <= to_date(#{endDate,jdbcType=VARCHAR},'yyyy-mm-dd hh24:mi:ss') order by b.SENDDATE ASC

select a.di_name,a.di_serialnum,b.* from (select t.*, row_number() over(partition by t.instartdate order by t.inenddate desc) rn from IOT_HISSEWAGECON_215 t where t.senddate >= to_date(#{startDate,jdbcType=VARCHAR},'yyyy-mm-dd hh24:mi:ss') and t.senddate <= to_date(#{endDate,jdbcType=VARCHAR},'yyyy-mm-dd hh24:mi:ss') ) b,iot_deviceinfo a where rn = 1 and a.di_serialnum=b.device_serialnum order by instartdate desc
